author: line0
name: DependencyControl Toolbox
description: Provides DependencyControl maintenance and configuration utilities.

0.1.1: The Install/Uninstall/Update dialogs now sort scripts by name.
DependencyControl and its requirements no longer appear in the uninstall menu.
0.1.2: All DependencyControl macros are now available under the common 'DependencyControl' automation submenu.
0.1.3: Fixed an issue where trying to uninstall an unmanaged script resulted in an error unrelated to the intended error message.
